# Cloudflare Pages — HTTP response headers
# Docs: https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/

# The Safe{Wallet} fetches the app manifest cross-origin to read its metadata,
# so it must be CORS-readable from any origin.
/manifest.json
  Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *

# Everything else: security hardening. frame-ancestors is the directive that
# matters for a Safe App — the app must be embeddable inside the Safe{Wallet}
# iframe (*.safe.global) and refused everywhere else.
/*
  Content-Security-Policy: frame-ancestors 'self' https://*.safe.global
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
